OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fshowers this evening, these briefly
OL,7,Fheavy in places, however some areas
OL,8,Fremaining mostly dry. Further showers
OL,9,Fovernight, occasionally heavy, mixed
OL,10,Fwith clear spells. Breezy at times and
OL,11,Fstaying rather windy in coastal
OL,12,Fregions. Remaining quite mild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FFrequent showers through the
OL,15,Fmorning, with possible thunder. Drier
OL,16,Fby the afternoon with warm sunny
OL,17,Fspells developing. Generally rather
OL,18,Fwindy and cool but warmer inland and
OL,19,Fin the sunnier moments.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
