OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMuch
OL,6,Fdrier on Friday with sunny intervals
OL,7,Fand isolated showers. Unseasonably
OL,8,Fwindy for some overnight with
OL,9,Fsoutherly gales possible on coasts.
OL,10,FOften breezy over the weekend with
OL,11,Frain at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
